      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you before you consider making a purchase. The exterior has seen better days \u2014 expect significant rust, multiple dents, deep scratches, and paint that is faded or peeling in numerous areas. The interior is worn and damaged, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require serious attention: it runs rough, has noticeable fluid leaks, and several systems are not functioning properly. This vehicle is best suited for a dedicated DIY mechanic, a parts donor, or a restoration project \u2014 it is not recommended for daily driving in its current state. We are pricing it accordingly and encourage any serious buyer to inspect it in person before committing.",
