      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in fair condition, and we want to be completely upfront about what you're getting. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 you can expect visible scratches, minor dents, and some fading or dulling of the paint in certain areas. It's not a showroom car, but it's presentable and functional. The interior has seen regular use: the upholstery shows wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces, and there may be some scuffs or staining on the trim. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term \u2014 this is reflected honestly in the price. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're taking on. This is a solid opportunity for a buyer who wants a drivable vehicle at an accessible price point and is comfortable with a project or everyday driver that isn't perfect.",
